UPDATE `l9n7b_product_lang` SET description='<p><strong>HERO GREEN – Vibrant Power Wig</strong></p>\n<p>Unleash your inner hero with this striking <strong>HERO GREEN</strong> wig, a bold statement piece in a vivid green shade. Designed for those who dare to stand out, this sleek, high-quality wig boasts a sharp bob cut with a smooth, silky texture, perfect for cosplay, stage performances, or avant-garde fashion. Whether you’re embodying a fierce comic book legend or making a futuristic fashion statement, this wig ensures all eyes are on you.</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>The elastic base has a circumference of 17" (42 cm) and goes up to 25" (63 cm). Of course, it can be made especially for you at the dimensions you prefer. Made in our small manufactory in Athens, Greece.</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>The actual shade of green may vary due to monitor display differences or slight variations in the raw material (polypropylene hair).</p>\n<p></p>', description_short='<p>A wig perfect for cosplay, stage performances, or avant-garde fashion. Whether you’re embodying a fierce comic book legend or making a futuristic fashion statement, this wig ensures all eyes are on you.</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>The elastic base has a circumference of 17" (42 cm) and goes up to 25" (63 cm). Of course, it can be made especially for you at the dimensions you prefer. Made in our small manufactory in Athens, Greece.</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>Actual shade of green may vary due to monitor display differences.</p>\n<p></p>', name='HERO GREEN', link_rewrite='hero-green' WHERE id_product=40 AND id_shop=1 AND id_lang=1;
